\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f1\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 First of all, Evan's health condition is in question. Although His disease won't be diagnosed until the last book in the series, this serves as a slow buildup to the reader so they can start to sense that something is wrong.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 The conversation about Sarah's pendant shows that doing something that unique in that special was truly out of Evan's comfort zone, thus giving more power to the idea that he truly sees Sarah as the one. This is relevant, because he ends up proposing and marrying her before book 1 is complete.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 Discussion of the one gift tradition are to help the readers understand Sarah's family dynamic a little better. There also a bunch of subtle points made throughout this family dinner scene.}
